<GUIClass name="INV_ProformaCritTrxUnitsForm" id="2aa7a55c-be0d-4324-8a24-87298bc634b5">
    <superclass name="CMUI_Modal"/>
    <transient/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>An option in the cash and invoice pro forma criteria is to specify the number of transactions of each selected type to create (by default it is 1).
This screen is reached from the Units button on the INV_ProformaCriteriaForm and allows specifying this number for each selected transaction type.</text>
